    <releaseNotes>
      - Initial release of EntityFrameworkCore.PolicyEnforcement.
    </releaseNotes>

    <tags>EntityFrameworkCore, EntityFramework, EF, Interceptor, PolicyEnforcement, .NET, DependencyInjection, efcore, policy, access-control, authorization, security</tags>

